        <abstract> 
<p>Has been "deeply interested by the great book" [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">11966</hi>]. Asks permission to publish extracts.</p> 
            <p>Did Dr Darwin go to Edinburgh when his son, Charles, died? Asks whether RD has ever heard a story about Dr Darwin that had been told to CD by the Galtons.</p>
